snippet.title: Madou Monogatari: Honou no Sotsuenji (PC Engine) - Gameplay
snippet.description: I believe this was the final remake of the first Madou Monogatari game.  Everythings way advanced and updated...the only thing I don't like about it is the voice acting.  It's good in and of itself, but it locks the textbox until it's done; you can't skip anything or end prematurely while the voices are still going.
